Date Related Functions
========================


1) To Print Current Date we can use the Below Command 

SELECT CURRENT_DATE();

+----------------+
| CURRENT_DATE() |
+----------------+
| 2025-12-26     |
+----------------+






2) To Print Current Time we can use the Below Command 

SELECT CURRENT_TIME();

+----------------+
| CURRENT_TIME() |
+----------------+
| 23:44:23       |
+----------------+






3) If we want to get Both Today’s Date & Time then we can use Below Command 

SELECT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP();

+---------------------+
| CURRENT_TIMESTAMP() |
+---------------------+
| 2025-12-26 23:46:25 |
+---------------------+








